Catch LLM artifacts (CLAUDE.md, Co-authored-by trailers, .cursorrules, etc.) in your codebase.

Usage:
  llm-lint [command]

Available Commands:
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  help        Help about any command
  hook        Install, uninstall, or inspect the llm-lint pre-commit hook
  rules       List or describe rules
  scan        Scan a repository for LLM artifacts
  version     Print version

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for llm-lint

Use "llm-lint [command] --help" for more information about a command.
